'''''Skeleton Coast''''' ni filime y’intambara y’abacanshuro yo muri 1987 yakozwe na John Cardos muri firime eshatu za mbere kuri producer Harry Alan Towers . Nibwo bwambere muri Towers 'Breton Film Productions.

== Umugambi ==
Mugihe cy'intambara yo muri [[Angola]] umukozi wa CIA Michael Smith akorana ninyeshyamba za UNITA. Yafashwe n’ingabo za [[Angola]], yoherezwa muri gereza kugira ngo abazwe n’umudage w’iburasirazuba witwa Major Schneider. Se wa Smith, Koloneli Bill Smith wahoze mu kiruhuko cy'izabukuru Colonel Bill Smith ntabwo yizera leta ya [[Amerika]] kurekura umuhungu we. Koloneli yagiye muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo y'uburengerazuba]] aho yishyuye Elia amayobera kugirango amenye amakuru yukuri kubyerekeye umuhungu we aho yari ari imbohe. Colonel Smith aha akazi abacanshuro barindwi azajyana muri [[Angola]] gutabara umuhungu we.

Kapiteni Simpson, umuyobozi w’inzego zishinzwe umutekano z’ikirombe cya diyama afite umugabo uhanze amaso Coloneli atinya ko ashobora kuba akora magendu ya diyama. Umugore wa Elia, Opal akomeje kugirana umubano utemewe na Simpson amumenyesha ko Coloneli yishe umuntu w’umutekano we, mu byukuri yishwe na Rick Weston, umuyobozi w’ingabo bwite za Smith. Rick yamenyesheje Coloneli ko yari umukozi wibanga wa [[Angola]]. Elia yahise amenya ko Col. Smith yamwishyuye amafaranag yamiganano.

Binjiye muri Angola, abacanshuro bafatanya na Sekassi, umuyobozi wo mu bwoko bwa Jonas Savimbi w’inyeshyamba kugira ngo bashyigikire gutabara Michael Smith.

